---
title: Sweet and Sticky Chicken Gyozas with Stir-Fried Veg and Jasmine Rice
description: Pronounced gee-oh-zuh, you can find these delicious Japanese style dumplings filled with a mixture of minced meat and/or veg, but these ones are stuffed with chicken! Our Sweet and Sticky Chicken Gyozas are served alongside fragrant jasmine rice and stir-fried veg in a rice bowl inspired dish.
